# ecology idea credit: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ecological
[ ] grass now drops mixed seeds (mixed seeds most often wont grow into anything besides 95% grass, however, they have a chance to grow into a random regular crop)
[ ] you can find crops in the world in pathes like grass directly on the ground no tilled soil required (you still need to till soil to plant seeds)
[ ] carrot seeds & potato seeds (you can still plant a potato or a carrot)
[ ] pollination (works like bonemeal)
[ ] reward treating animals ethicly (large pasture, water accsessibilty, etc), ex: more yeald
[ ] grass blocks have a chance to grow short grass above them naturally - And short grass is able to grow into tall grass.
